        #### Installation
        ```bash
        $ [sudo] pip install django-context-extra-view
        ```
        
        #### Examples
        ```python
        from django_context_extra_view.views import ContextExtraViewMixin
        
        class View(ContextExtraViewMixin,...):
            context_extra = {"my_page":{"active":True}}
        ```
        
        ```html
        {% if my_page.active %}...{% endif %}
        ```
        
